            <!-- CTA card -->
            <div style="background:rgba(105,255,135,0.04);border:1px solid rgba(105,255,135,0.15);border-radius:16px;padding:2rem;text-align:center;position:relative;overflow:hidden;">
              <div style="position:absolute;top:-50px;right:-50px;width:200px;height:200px;background:radial-gradient(circle,rgba(105,255,135,0.06) 0%,transparent 70%);pointer-events:none;"></div>
              <h3 style="font-size:1.2rem;font-weight:800;color:#e2e0fc;margin-bottom:8px;">
                Quieres que monitorizemos esto cada mes?
              </h3>
              <p style="font-size:0.88rem;color:#c3c6d2;margin-bottom:20px;max-width:500px;margin-left:auto;margin-right:auto;line-height:1.6;">
                Conecta tus herramientas, elige tu plan, y recibe cada mes este analisis actualizado con datos reales, tendencias y un plan de accion priorizado.
              </p>
              <a href="/dashboard/onboarding" style="display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;background:#69ff87;color:#002108;padding:14px 32px;border-radius:9999px;font-weight:800;text-decoration:none;font-size:0.95rem;transition:all 0.15s;">
                <span class="material-symbols-outlined" style="font-size:20px;">rocket_launch</span>
                Empezar ahora
              </a>
              <p style="font-size:0.72rem;color:#8d909b;margin-top:14px;">Sin compromiso. Puedes cancelar en cualquier momento.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        </div><!-- END carousel-page #plan -->

        <!-- ================================================================
             Page 8 (mobile-only) - #cierre - CTA
        ================================================================ -->
        <div class="carousel-page mobile-only" id="cierre">
          <div style="display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;justify-content:center;text-align:center;min-height:60vh;gap:24px;padding:2rem 1rem;">
            <div style="width:56px;height:56px;border-radius:50%;background:rgba(105,255,135,0.12);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;">
              <span class="material-symbols-outlined" style="font-size:28px;color:#69FF87;">radar</span>
            </div>
            <div style="font-size:1.4rem;font-weight:800;color:#e2e0fc;letter-spacing:-0.02em;line-height:1.2;">
              Activa AION Radar para {domain}
            </div>
            <p style="font-size:0.88rem;color:#c3c6d2;line-height:1.6;max-width:400px;">
              Monitoriza estos KPIs semanalmente. Ve como evolucionan tu SEO, visibilidad IA y competidores con cada accion que tomes.
            </p>
            <div style="display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:10px;width:100%;max-width:320px;font-size:0.82rem;color:#c3c6d2;text-align:left;margin:0 auto;">
              <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;">
                <span class="material-symbols-outlined" style="font-size:16px;color:#69FF87;">trending_up</span>
                Evolucion semanal de todos tus KPIs
              </div>
              <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;">
                <span class="material-symbols-outlined" style="font-size:16px;color:#69FF87;">notifications_active</span>
